        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/COVID-protests-violence-attacks-journalists-Europe.png" alt="Violence at COVID-related protests across Europe included hostility and attacks directed at journalists" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;">Violence at COVID-related protests across Europe included hostility and attacks directed at journalists. Credits: International Press Institute and EPA-EFE/ Giuseppe Lami</p>
